casebody.data:
State of FLORIDA, plaintiff,
v.
State of GEORGIA. No. 142, Original. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 13, 2015.

Motion of the Special Master for allowance of fees and disbursements granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $70,245.52 for the period April 1, 2015, through August 31, 2015, to be paid equally by the parties.
